title: 152: The Walmart Haul Episode (August '21 Edition)
itunes:title: The Walmart Haul Episode (August '21 Edition)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa, Jamie & Mikey are taste-testing over a dozen items from Walmart, including beef bacon, shepherd’s pie, sauteed mushrooms in a pouch, nutpods, the best cold brew coffee you’ll ever try, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, there’s one item that you’re going to want to run to Walmart right now to buy ASAP!!! Here’s a hint: It’s a uniquely flavored mustard. So push play now, then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of the items mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: No exaggeration… This is our GREATEST WALMART HAUL YET!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
